  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-975270ad-b503-442b-aa36-64e155277b3d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bfcec18f-8deb-4487-991d-c3886b2eab66\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-358f93ff-cdae-4f53-b18c-c24df2aec669\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 35</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2e7d6604-54e0-4873-b44c-16665ac02db0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9486ccec-cbb5-49e2-a125-d9cd019e17a8\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6ec402ba-2626-4261-9fb7-ebde1bba39a3\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a23120f0-74ae-4ae9-bf0b-245cfb269610\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 스토리보딩 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-46117c52-265b-4431-8e0c-e5f77241c80a\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7af636e7-1fa1-4f49-a535-32abdbb7493c\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 스토리보딩 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 하나하나 PPT 파일을 정리하도록 하겠습니다. 이제 시작입니다. 약 두달 뒤 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-74c810d2-65bf-4ca7-a528-7c5fbb066ffd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b138d697-2b8b-4430-9867-1f29465350fb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a214569f-b57a-4e0a-b060-9a5c471d6953\" style=\"color:#424242;\"><b>의심으로 가득 찬 마음은 승리로의 여정에 집중할 수 없다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-210caf68-c745-47c5-82f1-8226bc6e2c2d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1747843a-2170-469b-9628-42876bd3e9b7\" style=\"color:#888888;\"><b>A mind troubled by doubt cannot focus on the course to victory.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-31c6ba4b-8e1c-4803-abef-a97458d9b2b2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-51cd4e7a-0b35-43b9-b907-23b4183f5493\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3d9f277b-bfa5-4196-a9b3-b126a21ce25f\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-41989fa4-ed25-44ef-91e5-98088df64a29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-077d719a-197f-4827-b96e-fc129733b452\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-defa